title: Russell Westbrook’s Pass Between Defender’s Legs Is Probably The Best Play Of The NBA Season
text:
Shut it down, we have the best play of the NBA regular season. 
During tonight’s Thunder-Raptors game, OKC Thunder guard Russell Westbrook dtopped the nastiest dime of the season when he threw an insane pass threw a defender’s leg from about 20 feet away.
